{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completionHandler:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" (^)()) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The target coordinate to fit within the viewport."}]}],"name":"targetCoordinate"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":", the map animates to fit the target within the map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view. If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":", the map fits the target instantaneously.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"animated"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The block executed after the animation finishes."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"completion"}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, the target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"foci in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the target is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method has no effect if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userTrackingMode"},{"type":"text","text":" property is set to a value"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"other than "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:"}],"symbolKind":"method","title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L799","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:"},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the geographic coordinate that is the subject of observation as the user"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"location is being tracked, with an optional transition animation and completion"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"handler."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/settargetcoordinate:animated:completionhandler:"]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNMapView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView/setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","type":"topic","title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/settargetcoordinate:animated:completionhandler:","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setTargetCo